title: Before Common Era
description: Merging fashion and technology, Before Common Era (BCE)is known for its stand-out functional garments and accessories made for everyday usage. Their mission is to define what the future of fashion looks like by using emerging technology to change the way people view fashion while creating quality items. Thep erson that purchases BCE is family to a lifestyle that promotes an advanced and progressive approach to design.

title: Kitboys
description: Kitboys is a creative label that emphasizes footballing culture. Our purpose is to fuse and blur the lines between urban culture and sport. Propelling the game forward, while fully synthesizing the realms in which we grew up. Using our brands platform we will shift the emphasis from the players to the fans and supporting communities, thus pioneering a segment of futbol culture that has yet to be fully formed. Ultimately raising more awareness for the sport itself. We aim to provide a deeper understanding of culture and sport in a country where it is only analyzed on surface level.

title: Rise x Company
description: Rise X Company began as graphics led t-shirt company founded in 2011. Its first successes were through social media campaigns via Instagram, Facebook, and word of mouth. This led to a chance encounter with a local brick and mortar storefront boutique owner; that single-handedly catapulted Rise to popularity amongst the streetwear community within Arizona.

title: JackMove NYC
description: JackMove is a NYC brand. Mixing skate-life with fashion.

title: Few Less
description: Few Less an American street-wear brand, founded by Winter Frazier, in 2016 — Most notable for our heavily influenced athleisure aesthetics. We bring forth a mix of chic, minimalistic ready-to-wear collections. Few Less prides ourselves on detail, guaranteeing functional yet timeless garments brought to you through our lens.

title: MFBLU
description: MFBLU©️ IS A LUXURY MENSWEAR BRAND THAT EXPRESSES A SENTIMENTALITY FOR ART AND FASHION THROUGH THE STUDY OF PERSONAL AND HISTORICAL TECHNIQUES. MODERN WORKWEAR SILHOUETTES UNITED WITH FEMALE-CENTRIC TRADITIONS OF QUILTING, MENDING, PAINT STAINS AND APPLIQUÉ SHAPE THE COLLECTIONS. EACH PIECE TELLS A STORY AND IS TAILOR-MADE. THE BRAND BEGAN WITH A COLLECTION OF ONE-OF-A-KIND GARMENTS COMPOSED ENTIRELY OF VINTAGE AND DEADSTOCK TEXTILES AND CONTINUES TO REINVIGORATE AMERICAN MENSWEAR THROUGH THE ART OF STORYTELLING.

title: SubScript
description: Streetwear Brand from New York City.
